---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Timefold | Scheduling optimization platform">
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden border-b border-slate-200 bg-white">
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top,_rgba(99,102,241,0.16),_transparent_58%)]" aria-hidden="true" />
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-indigo-50/70 to-transparent" aria-hidden="true" />
    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-[1180px] px-4 pb-16 pt-14 sm:pb-28 sm:pt-28">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold leading-[1.07] tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-[3.25rem] lg:text-[4rem]">
          Optimize complex route, shift and task scheduling — one API call away
        </h1>
        <p class="mx-auto max-w-[46rem] text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-slate-600 sm:text-lg">
          The intelligent scheduling optimization platform for workforce management: route vehicles,
          schedule jobs, and assign employees optimally in real time.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-7 flex flex-col items-stretch justify-center gap-3 sm:mt-8 sm:flex-row sm:items-center">
          <a href="#start" class="rounded-full bg-slate-900 px-6 py-3 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition hover:bg-black">
            Request free trial
          </a>
          <a href="#models" class="rounded-full border border-slate-300 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 transition hover:border-slate-400 hover:text-slate-900">
            Explore our APIs
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/80 p-4 sm:mt-16 sm:p-5">
        <span class="eyebrow-label text-center text-[11px] text-slate-500">
          Trusted by enterprise teams
        </span>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-center text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6">
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-3 py-2.5">IBM</div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-3 py-2.5">Lufthansa</div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-3 py-2.5">NEC</div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-3 py-2.5">ADP</div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-3 py-2.5">Thales</div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-3 py-2.5">CBRE</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="solutions" class="border-b border-slate-200 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1180px] px-4 py-16 sm:py-24">
      <span class="eyebrow-label text-xs text-indigo-600">Solutions</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-[2.1rem]">Route, shift, and task scheduling optimization</h2>
      <p class="max-w-3xl text-sm text-slate-600">
        Choose the model that fits your business, then go from proof-of-concept to production quickly.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:mt-10 sm:gap-5 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm sm:p-7">
          <p class="eyebrow-label text-xs text-indigo-600">Route Scheduling Optimization</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Maximize productivity, minimize travel time</h3>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <li>Reduce travel time and operating cost</li>
            <li>Auto-generate optimal schedules and routes</li>
            <li>React instantly to day-to-day disruptions</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-500">
            <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-2.5 py-1">FIELD SERVICE</span>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-2.5 py-1">NEMT</span>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-2.5 py-1">LAST-MILE</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm sm:p-7">
          <p class="eyebrow-label text-xs text-violet-600">Shift Scheduling Optimization</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Balanced schedules, happier teams</h3>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <li>Improve shift coverage at scale</li>
            <li>Fair and balanced workday allocation</li>
            <li>Respect contracts, preferences and rules</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-500">
            <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-2.5 py-1">RETAIL</span>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-2.5 py-1">HOSPITALITY</span>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-2.5 py-1">HEALTHCARE</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm sm:p-7">
          <p class="eyebrow-label text-xs text-fuchsia-600">Task Scheduling Optimization</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Efficient sequences, optimal allocation</h3>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <li>Sequence jobs for higher throughput</li>
            <li>Assign resources with business constraints</li>
            <li>Increase predictability across operations</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-500">
            <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-2.5 py-1">PROJECTS</span>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-2.5 py-1">MAINTENANCE</span>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-2.5 py-1">MANUFACTURING</span>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-b border-slate-200 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1180px] px-4 py-16 sm:py-24">
      <span class="eyebrow-label text-xs text-indigo-600">Why Timefold</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-[2.1rem]">Your shortcut to world-class optimization</h2>
      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:mt-10 sm:gap-5 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">We handle the hard part</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Decades of optimization expertise packaged into practical APIs.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Start where others finish</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Skip years of risky solver development and launch fast.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Built for your reality</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Cover real constraints with extensibility for edge business rules.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">One-click optimization</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Keep your existing UX and workflows, add a schedule-with-AI action.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="models" class="border-b border-slate-200 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1180px] px-4 py-16 sm:py-24">
      <span class="eyebrow-label text-xs text-indigo-600">Planning Models</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-[2.1rem]">Real-world and ready-to-use APIs</h2>
      <p class="max-w-3xl text-sm text-slate-600">Get optimization out of the box. We took care of the complexity.</p>

      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:mt-10 sm:gap-5 md:grid-cols-3">
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm sm:p-7">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Field Service Routing</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Assign the right technician at the right time while minimizing travel.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm sm:p-7">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Employee Shift Scheduling</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Generate fair and compliant shifts across locations and roles.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm sm:p-7">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Last-Mile Delivery Routing</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Optimize depot-to-customer deliveries with capacity-aware routing.</p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:mt-8 sm:gap-5 md:grid-cols-3">
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm sm:p-7">
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">Always-on operations</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Plan months ahead and replan in real time when constraints change.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm sm:p-7">
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">Beat day-to-day chaos</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Handle absences, delays, emergencies and disruptions confidently.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm sm:p-7">
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">Balanced workdays</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Align schedules with skills, preferences, breaks and compliance rules.</p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 flex items-center justify-start">
        <a href="https://timefold.ai/model" class="rounded-full border border-slate-300 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 transition hover:border-slate-400 hover:text-slate-900">
          Explore models
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="intelligence" class="border-b border-slate-200 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1180px] px-4 py-16 sm:py-24">
      <div class="grid gap-6 sm:gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow-label text-xs text-indigo-600">Scheduling Intelligence</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-[2.1rem]">Timefold Intelligence</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
            Operational planning is step one. Add governance and insight with run-level intelligence and
            decision support.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <li>Run analytics for planner confidence and transparency</li>
            <li>Visibility into model quality, trade-offs and SLA impact</li>
            <li>Support faster decisions with actionable recommendations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-900 p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3">
            <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-800 p-3 text-xs text-slate-300">Coverage<br /><span class="text-lg text-white">99.2%</span></div>
            <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-800 p-3 text-xs text-slate-300">Travel Time<br /><span class="text-lg text-white">-24%</span></div>
            <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-800 p-3 text-xs text-slate-300">SLA Risk<br /><span class="text-lg text-white">Low</span></div>
            <div class="col-span-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-800 p-3 text-xs text-slate-300">
              Model run quality and fairness signals available for every planning cycle.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="proof" class="border-b border-slate-200 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1180px] px-4 py-16 sm:py-24">
      <span class="eyebrow-label text-xs text-indigo-600">Customer Stories</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-[2.1rem]">Proof in practice</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Their words, not ours.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:mt-10 sm:gap-5 md:grid-cols-3">
        <blockquote class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-7 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700 shadow-sm">
          “Timefold’s clean APIs and engineering-first approach made integration straightforward and fast.”
          <footer class="mt-4 text-xs text-slate-500">Technical Business Lead</footer>
        </blockquote>
        <blockquote class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-7 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700 shadow-sm">
          “We reduced time-to-market through a tight partnership and practical optimization support.”
          <footer class="mt-4 text-xs text-slate-500">Product Director</footer>
        </blockquote>
        <blockquote class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-7 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700 shadow-sm">
          “Operational with real data in days, not months, thanks to the platform foundation.”
          <footer class="mt-4 text-xs text-slate-500">Chief Architect</footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="pricing" class="border-b border-slate-200 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1180px] px-4 py-16 sm:py-24">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-10">
        <span class="eyebrow-label text-xs text-indigo-600">Pricing</span>
        <div class="mt-3 flex flex-col gap-4 sm:gap-5 md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-[2.1rem]">Simple model-based pricing</h2>
            <p class="max-w-2xl text-sm text-slate-600">
              Start with the model you need today, then scale to multiple models as your operations grow.
            </p>
          </div>
          <a href="#start" class="rounded-full bg-slate-900 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-black">
            Talk to sales
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="docs" class="border-b border-slate-200 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1180px] px-4 py-16 sm:py-24">
      <span class="eyebrow-label text-xs text-indigo-600">Platform</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-[2.1rem]">Solve on a single, powerful platform</h2>
      <p class="max-w-3xl text-sm text-slate-600">Leave admin, orchestration, scaling and upgrades to us.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:gap-5 md:grid-cols-3">
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Managed services</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Leave orchestration, scaling and upgrades to us.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Run insights</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Monitor quality and outcomes across model runs.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Multi-model support</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Operate routing, shifts and tasks in one platform.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-8 flex items-center justify-start">
        <a href="https://docs.timefold.ai" class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800 underline decoration-slate-300 underline-offset-4 transition hover:text-slate-900">
          Read documentation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="start" class="bg-slate-900">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1180px] px-4 py-16 sm:py-24">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-start justify-between gap-6 rounded-3xl border border-slate-700 bg-slate-950 px-6 py-8 sm:gap-8 sm:px-8 sm:py-10 md:flex-row md:items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight tracking-tight text-white">Get more out of your resources, fast</h2>
          <p class="max-w-2xl text-sm text-slate-300">Ready to start optimizing? Talk with our team to evaluate your use case.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="mailto:hello@timefold.ai" class="rounded-full bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 transition hover:bg-slate-200">
          Talk to us
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>